Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿숨바꼭질 할 사람\N여기 여기 붙어라~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.09,0:00:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,-할래~!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.87,0:00:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}나 같은 게...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.40,0:00:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}저 손가락에\N붙어도 되는 걸까...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.31,0:00:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}그렇게 고민하는 새에\N붙을 타이밍을 놓쳐서...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.10,0:00:13.21,Default - A,,0,0,0,,히토리쨩,\N왜 그러고 있니?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.61,0:00:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,800)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}정신이 들고 보면\N떨거지처럼 혼자만 남는 아이...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.80,0:00:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}소풍 때...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.00,0:00:20.50,Default - A,,0,0,0,,여기요~♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.65,0:00:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}선생님이랑 도시락 반찬을\N바꿔 먹던 외톨이 아이
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.15,0:00:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,다녀왔습니다
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.39,0:00:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}부활동에\N들지도 않고
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.13,0:00:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}방과 후에는\N바로 집에 옴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.93,0:00:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.46,0:00:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}스마트폰에\N오는 거라곤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.38,0:00:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}부모님이 보낸 메시지나\N쿠폰 알림이 끝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.72,0:00:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}그게 바로 나
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.51,0:00:48.00,Default - Right,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1880,1040)\fad(500,500)\fna두리둥실\fs45\bord5\blur0\c&HAD45FF&\3c&HF6F6F6&}※ 히토리 고토 : 혼잣말
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.81,0:00:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}고토 히토리
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.23,0:00:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}중학교 1학년
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.54,0:00:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}가~끔\N이런 생각이 들곤 해
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.59,0:00:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}이대로 살아도\N괜찮은 걸까, 하고
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.74,0:00:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}하지만 나는...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.19,0:00:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}말 붙이기도 전에\N「앗」하고 말이나 더듬고
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.85,0:00:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}눈 마주치는 것도\N어려운데다
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.10,0:01:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,800)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}The 아싸 캐릭같은 나날이\N내 주제에 잘 맞긴 해서...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.87,0:01:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,이거 보고 있니?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.12,0:01:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,아니~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.91,0:01:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur4\c&HFCFFC1&\3c&HF23523&}학창 시절 때는...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.37,0:01:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur4\c&HFCFFC1&\3c&HF23523&}교실 구석에서\N책 읽는 척이나 하는 놈이었죠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.01,0:01:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur4\c&HFCFFC1&\3c&HF23523&}친구도 없고...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.62,0:01:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur4\c&HFCFFC1&\3c&HF23523&}그런 분께서 지금은!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur4\c&HFCFFC1&\3c&HF23523&}젊은이들한테 절대적인 인기를\N자랑하는 밴드가 되셨군요!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.75,0:01:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur4\c&HFCFFC1&\3c&HF23523&}뭐...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.58,0:01:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur4\c&HFCFFC1&\3c&HF23523&}밴드는 아싸라도\N빛날 수 있는 곳이라
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.15,0:01:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur4\c&HFCFFC1&\3c&HF23523&}그렇군요~!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.43,0:01:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur4\c&HFCFFC1&\3c&HF23523&}그럼, 들어주시죠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.54,0:01:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur4\c&HFCFFC1&\3c&HF23523&}「In Storms」가 부릅니다
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.10,0:01:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,600)\blur4\c&HFCFFC1&\3c&HF23523&}「방아쇠」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.60,0:01:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,어우...\N왜 그러니?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.12,0:01:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 아빠!\N기타 빌려줘!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.48,0:01:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,어...?\N괜찮지...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.20,0:01:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,고..고마워!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.24,0:01:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,그렇구나~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.44,0:01:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,히토리도 마침내\N기타에 흥미를~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.47,0:01:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}밴드를 결성하면...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.14,0:01:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}나 같은 인간이라도...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.95,0:01:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,600)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}혹시\N반짝일 수 있나!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.00,0:02:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,결심했어!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.06,0:02:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,기타\N잘 치게 될 거야!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.27,0:02:12.27,Default - Left,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,300)\fna하얀구름\b0\fs50\frz11.13\pos(655,225)\c&H6259D9&\3c&HE7F7F6&}처음 시작하는\N일렉기타
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.44,0:02:14.15,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,10)\fna천생연분\b1\fs40\bord7\c&H6259D9&\3c&HE8E7F0&\frz17.96\pos(1076.334,97)}로우 코드를 마스터하자
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.44,0:02:14.15,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,10)\fna천생연분\b1\fs40\bord3\c&H6259D9&\3c&H36325B&\frz17.96\pos(1076.334,97)}로우 코드를 마스터하자
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.97,0:02:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,그래서\N학교에서 밴드 결성하고~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.80,0:02:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,E...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.55,0:02:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,E, A...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.46,0:02:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,E, A, G...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.52,0:02:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,왜 갑자기\N영어가 튀어나옴...??
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.73,0:02:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,그래서 문화제에서\N라이브도 하고...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.52,0:02:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,모두한테\N찬양받는 거야~!
