Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.17,0:09:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,여보세요~?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.31,0:09:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}마...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.90,0:09:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}말하는 게 너무 오랜만이라\N목소리가...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.84,0:09:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,느닷없이 말 걸어서\N미안해!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.48,0:09:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,난 시모키타자와 고교\N2학년, 이지치 니지카!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.05,0:09:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,아...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,고토 히토리\N슈카 고교 1학녀{\fs60}님{\fs50}미{\fs40}다...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.61,0:09:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,궁금해서 그런데\N히토리쨩은 말야~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.97,0:09:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}느닷없이\N말 놓네!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.50,0:09:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,기타\N얼마나 칠 줄 알아?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.27,0:09:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 그럭저럭\N칠 거 같긴 한데...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.42,0:09:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,그렇구나!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.69,0:09:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,저..저기 말야!\N지금 좀 곤란한 상황이라...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.28,0:09:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,안 되겠다면\N괜찮긴 한데~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.53,0:09:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,괜찮긴 한데에\N진짜 곤란해서어~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.33,0:09:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}딱 봐도\N안 괜찮은 거~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.51,0:09:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,응!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.34,0:09:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,미친 척 하고\N말해버리자!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.20,0:09:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs90}부탁이야!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.58,0:09:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,내 밴드에서!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.70,0:09:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,오늘만 서포트 기타\N뛰어주면 안 될까~!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.44,0:09:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}밴드...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.56,0:10:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,이제 곧 라이브 있는데\N기타 애가 갑자기 관둬버려서~!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.30,0:10:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,어느 정도 칠 줄만 알면\N바로 할 수 있는 곡이니까~!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.91,0:10:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&\fs90}지금부터!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.96,0:10:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&\fs110}라이브???!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.24,0:10:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,아무쪼록~!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.01,0:10:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,아...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.63,0:10:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,아니이...
