Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.67,0:10:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,고맙고~!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.52,0:10:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,당장\N라이브 하우스로 GO!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.28,0:10:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}아직 아무 말도\N안 했어!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:17.93,Default - Right,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fna하얀구름\b0\fs80\bord0\blur1\frx12\fry346\frz20.16\pos(1255,915)}시모키타자와역
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.14,0:10:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}와버리고 말았다...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.02,0:10:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,히토리쨩은\N시모키타 자주 와~?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.47,0:10:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 아니...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.83,0:10:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}이런 개성 넘치는 멋쟁이 타운에\N올 수 있을 리가 없지...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.83,0:10:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,라이브 하우스는\N좀만 가면 도착하니까!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.58,0:10:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}니지카쨩은\N참 멋쟁이네...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.00,0:10:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}이거야말로\N딱 밴드녀란 느낌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}그에 비해 나는\N고구마 츄리닝에
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.89,0:10:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}다크서클\N오지는데다
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.74,0:10:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}등까지 굽어서...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.26,0:10:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}아...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.94,0:10:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}나, 곰팡내 날지도...\N항상 벽장에서 지내니까...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.76,0:10:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}아니,\N방충제 냄새네
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.51,0:10:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}그에 비해 니지카쨩\N냄새 열라 좋다~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.47,0:10:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}원래 여고생이\N지녀야 할 향기다~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.56,0:10:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,걷는 페이스가\N빨랐나?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.99,0:10:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 아뇹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.24,0:11:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,오늘 출연할 라이브 하우스는\N「STARRY」라고 하는데 말야!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.11,0:11:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,우리 언니가\N점장을 하고 있어서~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.52,0:11:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}출연할 라이브 하우스...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.09,0:11:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}뭔가 그럴싸한 어감...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.27,0:11:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}어라?\N어째 심장이 큰일났...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,그래서 있지!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.64,0:11:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,내가 거기서\N알바 하는데~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.15,0:11:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,히토리쨩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.15,0:11:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,사실 운동 좀\N잘 하고 그래?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.31,0:11:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,아뇻...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.01,0:11:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 그..그래도...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.82,0:11:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,피구만큼은 어째선지\N항상 마지막까지 남곤 했어요...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.22,0:11:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,그, 그렇구나...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.30,0:11:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}내가 라이브 하우스에서\N연주를...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.63,0:11:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}아, 아아아...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.98,0:11:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}안 되지, 안 돼!\N지금 약한 먹으면!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.03,0:11:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}떠올려라...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.87,0:11:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}망상에서 매일같이 해왔던\N문화제 라이브를...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.25,0:11:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}그리고\N첫 원맨 라이브!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.93,0:11:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}ZIPPER...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.82,0:11:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,1000)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&\fs100\pos(960,980)}슈퍼 아레나~!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.03,0:11:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,1000)\blur5\pos(960980)}-히토리, 히토리, 히토리…!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.29,0:11:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,나는 무도관조차\N가득 채웠던 여자...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.75,0:11:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,에!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.67,0:11:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 아뇨...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.25,0:11:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}부탁할 상대를 잘못 골랐다고\N생각하지 않기를~!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.59,0:11:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur3\c&HCACACA&}부탁할 상대를\N잘못 골랐나...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.29,0:11:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,다 왔다!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:11:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,여기양~♪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.51,0:12:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}마...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.31,0:12:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}마경...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.35,0:12:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,좋은 아침입니다~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.25,0:12:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}첫 라이브 하우스...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.65,0:12:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}이 어둑함...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.43,0:12:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}압박감...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.11,0:12:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}아, 차분해진다~!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.20,0:12:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,히토리쨩, 괜찮아?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.62,0:12:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 우리집이다~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.22,0:12:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,아닌데!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.00,0:12:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,이번에도 PA 씨네한테\N영상 부탁할까~?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.36,0:12:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,오늘 같이 공연할\N밴드구나!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.61,0:12:25.58,Default - A,,0,0,0,,우리보다 연상이려나?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.58,0:12:28.44,Default - A,,0,0,0,,쟤네가 끝나면\N우리 리허설이니까!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.39,0:12:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}밴드라고 하면\N어째 꼭 무섭단 이미지가 있는데
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.41,0:12:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}어차피\N인도어들의 집합!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.02,0:12:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}어둠의 자식들!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.81,0:12:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}아싸 집단!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.84,0:12:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}다들 나랑 똑같이...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.26,0:12:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,저기 있는 게~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.31,0:12:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,PA 씨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.98,0:12:34.56,Default - Right,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fna시골b\fs70\bord5\fscx80\c&H52EAEC&\3c&H293C42&\frx0\fry358\frz0.3613\pos(1500,905)}기재 파손 원인이 되오니 드링크 등은 절대 흩뿌리지 마세요!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.30,0:12:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,안녕하세요...
