Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.32,0:12:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,이제야 돌아왔네
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.79,0:12:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,료~!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.49,0:12:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,얘는\N고토 히토리쨩!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.60,0:12:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,기적적으로 공원에 있던\N기타리스트야~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.37,0:12:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,헤에...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.52,0:12:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}무섭...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.27,0:12:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}노려보는 건가!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.89,0:12:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,얘는 베이스를 맡고 있는\N야마다 료야~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.15,0:12:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,고고고토 히토리입니다!\N대단히 죄송합니다!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.98,0:12:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,어, 잠깐...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.22,0:12:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,괜찮다니까~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:12:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,료는 표정이\N잘 안 드러나는 것뿐!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.85,0:13:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,괴짜라고 하면\N기뻐한다~?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.83,0:13:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,하나도 안 기쁘거든~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.31,0:13:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}기뻐 보이네...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.82,0:13:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,그러고 보니\N점장님이...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.15,0:13:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,어!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.90,0:13:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,공연 시간까지\N연습해두래
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.12,0:13:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,그리고 니지카가 멋대로\N라이브 하우스 뛰쳐나간 걸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.92,0:13:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,화내면서\N물건 사러 나갔어
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.44,0:13:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,히익, 거짓말!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.91,0:13:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,돌아오기 전에\N스튜디오로 가자...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,히토리쨩도~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,얼른!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.72,0:13:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 네...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.45,0:13:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}현실은 무섭다...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.72,0:13:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}하지만...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.68,0:13:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}앞으로 즐거운 일들이\N잔뜩 기다리고 있을 것만 같아...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.89,0:13:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,받아!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.57,0:13:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,오늘 세트 리스트랑\N악보!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.56,0:13:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 저기...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,밴드 멤버는...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.21,0:13:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,이걸로 끝이야~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,우리는\N이번에 Inst. 밴드니까!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.67,0:13:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}응...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.78,0:13:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}이 곡이라면\N할 수 있겠어!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.81,0:13:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}하지만 보컬이 없는만큼\N연주를 열심히 해야 할 텐데...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.35,0:13:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}난 기타 잘 친다고들 하니까\N할 수 있어...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}할 수 있을걸...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.43,0:13:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur3\c&HCACACA&}고릴라...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.40,0:14:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}연주를 들으면\N둘 다 깜짝 놀랄지도~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.73,0:14:02.84,Default - A,,0,0,0,,바로 시작할까 하는데~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.84,0:14:04.87,Default - A,,0,0,0,,처음부터 쳐볼까?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.87,0:14:07.27,Default - A,,0,0,0,,뭐, 처음이니까\N조금 느긋하게 치다가
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.27,0:14:09.51,Default - A,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,600)}그 다음에 서서히\N손에 익히는 느낌으로~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.68,0:14:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}그야\N인터넷에서는 꽤나...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.64,0:14:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}아니,\N제법 평가 좋으니깐...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.14,0:14:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}구독자수\N3만도 찍었구...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.99,0:14:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}좋았어어...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.21,0:14:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}해주마~!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.96,0:14:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,그럼, 간다♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,졸라 못 친다...!
