Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.02,0:15:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960.72,980.38)}여여여역시\N못하겠어요!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.06,0:15:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(959.27,979.67)}여여여역시\N못하겠어요!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.10,0:15:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(959.81,980.98)}여여여역시\N못하겠어요!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.14,0:15:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960.18,979.1)}여여여역시\N못하겠어요!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.18,0:15:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960.43,979)}여여여역시\N못하겠어요!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.22,0:15:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(959.4,979.08)}여여여역시\N못하겠어요!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.27,0:15:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960.67,979.07)}여여여역시\N못하겠어요!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960.65,980.54)}여여여역시\N못하겠어요!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.35,0:15:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960.06,979.1)}여여여역시\N못하겠어요!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(959.87,979.67)}여여여역시\N못하겠어요!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.43,0:15:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960.58,980.05)}여여여역시\N못하겠어요!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.47,0:15:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(959.05,980.81)}여여여역시\N못하겠어요!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.52,0:15:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(959.84,979.5)}여여여역시\N못하겠어요!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.56,0:15:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,어쩔 수 없잖아\N즉석 밴드인데!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.28,0:15:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,나도 그닥\N잘 치진 못하니까!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.50,0:15:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,난 잘 치지!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.97,0:15:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,헤, 헤헤헤...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.32,0:15:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,아무튼\N여기 좀 보자~!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.43,0:15:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,현실도피 하지 말고~!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.38,0:15:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(822,980)}에..MC에서도\N전혀 도움이 안 될 텐데...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.74,0:15:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(768,980)}아..아하하하하!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.76,0:15:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(768,980)}제 목숨으로\N할복 쇼라도~!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.48,0:15:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(768,980)\fad(00,1000)}배..밴드 이름 정도는\N다들 외우고 가주실지도...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.47,0:15:40.25,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,00)\blur5\pos(418,365)}존나 못 쳐서\N죄송합니다!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.25,0:15:41.50,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,700)\blur5\pos(418,365)\c&H000000&\3c&H0000FF&}존나 못 쳐서\N죄송합니다!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,너무 Rock하다...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.41,0:15:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,걱정 마
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.51,0:15:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,히토리가 야유받으면\N내가 베이스로
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.75,0:15:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,뽐~\N해버릴 테니까
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.50,0:15:46.92,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,730)\fn양재매화체S\fs90\bord6\c&H3200DB&\3c&HEBEBEB&\frz14.35\pos(848,434)}뽐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.18,0:15:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,베..베이스가...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.33,0:15:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,그런 깜찍한 소리가\N나오려나요...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.73,0:15:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,유혈 사태가 벌어지는 것도\NRock하니까
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.71,0:15:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Rock이니까
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.64,0:15:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Rock이\N너무 만능 면죄부인데!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.85,0:15:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,게다가~!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.78,0:16:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,우리 밴드를 보러 오는 건\N아마 내 친구밖에 없을 테니까!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.23,0:16:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,에...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.11,0:16:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,난 친구가\N니지카밖에 없으니까
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.79,0:16:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,평범한 여고생이\N연주를 잘하니 못하니~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.49,0:16:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,그런 걸\N어떻게 알겠냐구!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.84,0:16:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}불판날 거 같은\N발언...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.67,0:16:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(590,980)}알겠지?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.25,0:16:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(590,980)}그러니까\N안심하셔~!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.18,0:16:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(590,980)}그렇게 말씀하셔도...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.83,0:16:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(590,980)}난 좋은지 나쁜지\N알 수 있지만!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.58,0:16:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(590,980)}료는\N정상이 아니니까
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.15,0:16:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(590,980)}헤...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.00,0:16:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(590,980)}에헤헤헤...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.67,0:16:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(590,980)}아니, 기뻐하지 마\N기뻐하지 마...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.88,0:16:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,죄송해요...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,그래도...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.81,0:16:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,강요할 일은 아니지
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,그러네...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.12,0:16:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,억지로 부탁해서\N미안해!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.70,0:16:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 아니\N그 부분은...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.12,0:16:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(590,980)}저..정말로 기뻤어요...\N말 걸어주셔서...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.74,0:16:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,밴드는 쭉 결성하고 싶다고\N생각했었으니까...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.59,0:16:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 그..그래도\N메..멤버가 안 모여서...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.47,0:16:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,그래서, 평소에는\N커버곡을 인터넷에 올리거나...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.65,0:16:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,평소에는\N뭘 치는데?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.22,0:16:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,아...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.76,0:16:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,결성했을 때\N바로 대응할 수 있게...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.31,0:16:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,요 몇 년간\N히트 친 밴드 곡은 대충 다...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.32,0:16:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,헐, 쩔어!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.32,0:16:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(590,980)}아뇨, 전혀...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.86,0:16:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(590,980)}결국\N이런 꼬라지라...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(590,980)}역시 저로서는\N누군가랑 밴드를 한다는 건...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.31,0:17:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,팔리는 곡\N커버만 쳤다니...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.52,0:17:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,어째\N기타 히어로 씨 같다?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.81,0:17:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,근데, 알아?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.99,0:17:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,아마 우리랑\N나이 차이도 얼마 안 날 텐데
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.39,0:17:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}기타 히어로...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.63,0:17:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}어, 나!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.10,0:17:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,모른다면\N나중에 URL 보내줄게!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.60,0:17:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,진짜 최고로 잘 치니까\N꼭 들어봐!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.28,0:17:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}최고오오~?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.09,0:17:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,나도 추천 영상으로\N계속 올라오니까 본 적 있는데
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.84,0:17:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,엄청 잘 쳤어
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.25,0:17:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,그치!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.12,0:17:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,네이밍 센스는\N좀 안습하지만~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.79,0:17:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}안습해...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:37.66,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fna천생연분\fs40\c&H6A5DD4&\3c&HE8EAF2&\frx340\fry340\frz346.2\pos(1133,780)}타는 쓰레기
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.98,0:17:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,나, 팔로우해서\N알림도 켜뒀거든~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,언젠가 같이\N연주해보고 싶다~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.86,0:17:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}방금 하셨는데 말이죠~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.33,0:17:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,어, 그러니까 있지
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.39,0:17:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,무슨 말을\N하고 싶은 거냐면...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,잘 치고\N화제가 되는 사람도 말야
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.20,0:17:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,우리가 안 보는 데서\N잔뜩, 잔~뜩!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.50,0:17:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,기타를 쳐 왔겠지\N..라는 소리!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.46,0:17:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,나중에\N한 번 봐봐!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.89,0:17:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,영상을 보면\N전해져 올 테니까!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.74,0:17:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}현실 세계의 사람들은...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.02,0:18:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}아무도 나 따위한테는\N흥미 없을 줄 알았어...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.54,0:18:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,오늘 실패했다고 해서\N밴드 포기하긴 이르다니까!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.07,0:18:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,우리가 좀 거시기\N했을 뿐이었을지도 모르고...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.44,0:18:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,거시기?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,히토리쨩?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.16,0:18:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}그래도, 이렇게 다정한 사람이\N계속 지켜봐줬고
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.94,0:18:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}나 같은 거한테\N말까지 걸어줬잖아!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.25,0:18:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,어, 일어섰다
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.87,0:18:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}이런 기적...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.19,0:18:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}아마 평생\N안 일어날 거야...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.96,0:18:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}절대 날려먹어선\N안 돼...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.69,0:18:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,저..저, 그게...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.14,0:18:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,혹시 나가줄 생각이\N들었다든가...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.03,0:18:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,히, 히토리쨩?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.65,0:18:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}머리로는 알고 있어!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.33,0:18:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}하지만\N역시 무서워~!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.85,0:18:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}관객들의 시선도\N견딜 수 있을 리가~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.76,0:18:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,무섭다면\N여기 들어가서 연주하든가?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.31,0:18:48.56,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fna뉴궁서m\fs100\bord6\c&H3F45BF&\3c&HDBE3EB&\pos(1185,425)}완숙 {\fna피오피동글\b0}망고
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.62,0:18:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,평소 치는 환경이랑\N똑같아요오오
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.28,0:18:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,어떤 데서 살길래...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.73,0:18:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,여러분~!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.48,0:18:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,시모키타를\N뜨겁게 달궈봅시다~!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.74,0:18:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,조금 배짱이 커졌다...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.52,0:18:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,그러고 보니까
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.48,0:18:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,라이브에서\N뭐라고 소개하면 돼?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.56,0:19:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,히토리쨩?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.71,0:19:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,본명이면 될까?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.23,0:19:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,아..아니, 그건...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,그럼\N별명 같은 건 없어?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,주..중학교 때는\N"저기~" 라든가
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.26,0:19:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,"어이"라든가...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.32,0:19:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,그건\N별명이 아니지 않아!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.88,0:19:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,벼..별명으로 부를만큼\N친한 교우관계는 가져본 적이~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.16,0:19:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,히토리...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.41,0:19:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,히토리봇치...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.41,0:19:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\bord3\pos(936,908)}외톨이
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.12,0:19:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치쨩은 어때?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.36,0:19:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,헐, 설마 그런\N민감할 부분을...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.40,0:19:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,보...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.60,0:19:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,보, 보...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.78,0:19:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,보, 보, 보...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.98,0:19:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,보, 보, 보, 보...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.55,0:19:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs90}봇치예요!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.35,0:19:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,기뻐하는데, 뭐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.49,0:19:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,별명으로 불리는 건\N처음이라~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.76,0:19:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,왠지 눈에\N습기 차기 시작했어...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.39,0:19:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 아직 밴드명을\N못 들었네요
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.88,0:19:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,으윽...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.92,0:19:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.25,0:19:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,결속 밴드야
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.12,0:19:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,790)}결속 밴드...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.27,0:19:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,790)}케이블 타이??
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.56,0:19:40.82,Default - Right,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1880,1040)\fad(500,10)\fna두리둥실\fs45\bord5\c&H4C9ED8&}※ 글자가 그냥 똑같음
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,푸흡~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.90,0:19:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,걸작이야...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.76,0:19:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,하나도\N안 재밌거든!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.53,0:19:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,내가 죽어도\N바꿔버릴 거니까~!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.88,0:19:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,왜?\N귀엽지?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.57,0:19:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 네...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.11,0:19:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,밴드명은 나중에 생각하고!\N슬슬 나가자구!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.23,0:19:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,괜찮아!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.89,0:19:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,실력은\N좀 안 돼도...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.88,0:19:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,즐겁게 치자는 것만은\N명심하자!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.66,0:20:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,사운드란 건 굉장히\N감정이 드러나기 쉬우니까
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.03,0:20:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 네...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,기술을 추구하는 건\N다음부터 해도 완전 괜찮아!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.35,0:20:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}"다음"이라니...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.57,0:20:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,좋아, 가자!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.78,0:20:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,응
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.84,0:20:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}나...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.99,0:20:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,600)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}다음에도 있어도\N되는구나...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.39,0:20:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,처음 뵙겠습니다~!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.53,0:20:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,결속 밴드입니다~!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.31,0:20:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,오늘은 여러분도 아마 알고 있을\N곡을 몇 곡인가 칠 테니까
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.33,0:20:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,들어주세요!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.88,0:20:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,저건 또 누군데?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.43,0:20:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}평소 실력도 못 내서\N최악이지만...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.66,0:20:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}밴드 결성해서\N누군가랑 연주하는 게...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.67,0:20:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}이렇게나 즐거웠구나!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.64,0:20:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}나, 오늘\N최고로 빛나―!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.64,0:20:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&\fs100}..지 않잖아!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.84,0:20:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,800)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}오히려 인생에서\N제일 비참할지도오오!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,싹 다 틀려먹었네~!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.96,0:21:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,MC까지 조졌지
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.40,0:21:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,에헤...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.92,0:21:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,저..저기!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.63,0:21:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,뭔데...!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.16,0:21:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,뭐야!?\N무서운데요...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.48,0:21:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,다음 라이브 때까지는
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.63,0:21:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,반 애들한테 인사할 수 있을\N정도는 돼서 올게요!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.08,0:21:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,뭔 선언임??
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.49,0:21:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,눈부신 성장이구나~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.36,0:21:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,그래도 그렇구나...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.67,0:21:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,응!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.45,0:21:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,좋아~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.05,0:21:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,그럼 지금부터\N봇치쨩 환영회 겸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.09,0:21:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,라이브 반성회다~!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.71,0:21:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,아...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.35,0:21:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,오늘은 사람들이랑\N말 너무 많이 해서
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.55,0:21:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,피곤하니까\N돌아가겠습니다아
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.31,0:21:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,에...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.72,0:21:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,미안, 졸려
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.82,0:21:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,에!?
